    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下教育平台的内容分发和成绩同步之间的依赖关系。核心模块有三个：ContentCDN、GradeSync 和 LMS Portal。我想看看它们之间是怎么互相约束的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
