      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个核心模块。我先把 Education_ContentCDN 放在左边作为起点，您说的约束关系具体有哪些？是单向的还是双向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ContentCDN 会定义 GradeSync 的一些行为，但同时也会施加限制给 LMS Portal。另外 GradeSync 自身也有一些内部逻辑——它既允许某些操作，又禁止另一些操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出 ContentCDN 指向 GradeSync 的 defines 关系，以及指向 LMS Portal 的 imposes 关系。样式上我用统一的 box1 类，填充色用 #2a9fc9，字体 Avenir 14px。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "box1"
