    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有，ContentCDN 对 LMS Portal 其实有两层关系：imposes 是运行时限制，defines 是接口契约定义。这两个要分开画。",
      "elements_involved": [
